title: 20+ Funny Dating Memes for Gals and Pals Who Put the 'L' in LGBTQ
text: We're LGBTQ+ friendly over here, so if you're not, please, just go away. This list is for the L in LGBTQ+. We're talking WLW memes. So if you're wearing docs, rolled your pants up, have an "alternative" hairstyle, and recently listened to a Mitski song, welcome! I hope you like LOLing to your [dating probs](https://cheezburger.com/23798789/how-did-you-catch-them-cheating-monogamous-exes-share-spicy-situations-of-when-they-discovered-their), because these memes are really about to call you out. Oh, you date women? What's it like moving in with someone after not even dating for half a year? How many times have you tried to be glaringly obvious that you were interested in another girl but it turns out their straight and think you're just trying to be [besties](https://cheezburger.com/23751685/24-midnight-kiss-memes-for-besties-looking-for-love-this-new-years-eve)? What's it like dating your ex's ex? Ahhh yes, humor from heartbreak. What else are memes good for? So let's gather round, girlies, and LOL together to these painfully relatable dating memes for gals and pals who put the 'L' in LGBTQ+. Like what you see?
